quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  47,30,"Sinno Men haajuno, Men holleteno …ìe. Anndiraa …ìe maandeeji ma…ì…ìe …óin; ko pellet, a anndirayno …ìe ka konngol welngol. Allah non hino anndi golle mon …óen"
  47,31,"Ma Men jarribo on, haa Men annda tii…ónii…ìe …ìen e mon, e mu√±√±ii…ìe …ìen. Men jarriboo kadi kabaruuji mon"
  47,32,"Pellet, yeddu…ìe …ìen …ìe faddi laawol Allah ngol, …ìe lunndii Nulaa…óo on …ìaawo nde peewal ngal …ìanngannde …ìe, …ìen lorrataa Allah hay huunde. Ma O bonnu fii golle ma…ì…ìe …óen"
  47,33,"Ko onon yo gom…óim…ìe! ∆äoftee Allah, …óofto…óon Nulaa…óo on, wata on bonnu golle mon …óen"
  47,34,"Pellet, …ìen yeddu…ìe …ìe sakkii e laawol Allah ngol, hooti …ìe maayi ko …ìe heefer…ìe, Allah haforanoytaa …ìe"
  47,35,"Wata on lo'inkino, noddon e beldal, ko onon woni foolu…ìe …ìen, Allah no wonndi e mon, O ustantaa on njo…ìdi golle mon …óen"
  47,36,"Anndee nguurndam aduna ko fijindaaru e mbelee…óe tan; hara le si on gom…óiii, on hulii [Allah], O ye…óay on njo…ìdi mon ndin, o lamndotaako on jawle mon …óen"
  47,37,"Si O aru lamndaade on fii majje, haa O du√±ii on (e mun), wuddon, O fe√±√±ina non konnaagu mon ngun"
  47,38,"Hey mon onon …óoo, hi…óo noddee e nafqugol fii laawol Allah ngol. Hino e mo'on wudday…ìe. Kala non wuddu…óo, haray ko hoore-makko o wuddani. Ko Allah woni Galo On, onon won…óon waasu…ìe …ìen. Si on huccii, O wa…ótitira on wo…ó…ìe goo, hara non …ìen wa'ataa wano mon"
